{"hash":"fb5f43f994c6a3f4658dafa8e8ff80ad6e48f385","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"95d82bcf962b71caa6da2dbe0cf63701","title":"Introduction","description":"","path":"/docs/","timeToRead":2,"content":"<h1 id=\"introduction\"><a href=\"#introduction\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Introduction</h1>\n<p>ThreeFold has created the largest peer-to-peer cloud on the planet — but the internet is more than just storage and capacity. To fully realize the vision of an internet built for everyone, by everyone, we need easy-to-use and easy-to-deploy alternatives to the online tools and applications we use most. </p>\n<p>From publishing to video hosting, communication to project management, ThreeFold has developed a suite of turnkey solutions for end-users to create, share and build on the decentralized and secure ThreeFold Grid. </p>\n<p><strong>The internet of tomorrow, available today — this is ThreeFold Now.</strong>  </p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 2560 1935' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-31c8d74abfac70690401e99ba6418973'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-31c8d74abfac70690401e99ba6418973)' width='2560' height='1935' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAwCAYAAAChS3wfAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAOt0lEQVRo3uVaa2xc1RE2WEFC/OgPWlWKqoo/8LdSSaQEJGzUxAskcZCSSiU0agVUSJRCm5ZHKTHQiFZqKeJVtSUPBUgQCUQJEJzYju2YOLZJ/Ezs%2bO147fVz7X2/994zne/cO%2bu767VjO60qpUcancc9c%2bbMnDlzZma3oIBLSYmr4P%2btuFw2zzseeUTXGzdu/M7DpaWu0tLNri1bS10PlGxw7drzjmtfndu1v3bQ9VGDx/XxNxOug%2bfcrr01A659PIZ6f92w6%2b3jF1xbSre6Nm16yLV58%2ba8sGXLlusC5xqLrbs557sTNjGUlpY%2bUFJS8l3N%2b44dBQWb7i8uROfedeuf/dWDG%2bnxR9fTvTuKaO2atfSPf75P4XiKRjwT1D/kpiG3h/yhKCUNokTKpERa6XZXTx9t27aNiouLF4T77rvvuqCoqEiD1S7O6